{"tid":1064650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國截獲454噸中國走私豬肉 史上最大宗 憂非洲豬瘟傳入","createTime":"2019-03-16T17:05:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T12:27:58.000Z","uid":48083,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"19bad8b295864dd5e0262e882985de8c968e0470","tid":1064650,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T17:05:22.000Z","msg":"美國海關日前檢獲454噸中國走私豬肉。 (路透社)<br />\n美國海關及邊防局（Customs and Border Protection；CBP）15日宣佈，日前破獲美國史上最大宗農產品走私案。CBP在過去數周，在新澤西州檢獲454噸來自中國的走私豬肉及豬肉製品。中國的非洲豬瘟疫情尚未止息，美國憂慮走私豬肉或受非洲豬瘟病毒污染，影響美國豬農業。<br />\n<br />\nCBP在紐瓦克市港口發現逾50個藏有走私豬肉的貨櫃陸續運抵。不法之徒以各種方式，企圖混水摸魚，包括將一些含豬肉的食品，貼上「不含豬肉」的食物標籤；另有一些豬肉製品直接藏在裝有其他貨物的箱子內。<br />\n<br />\n美國目前尚未發現過非洲豬瘟。CBP地區主管米勒（Troy Miller）表示，若中國的非洲豬瘟疫情流入美國並擴散，一年可造成高達100億美元（約785億港元）的損失。<br />\n<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n-------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190316/59375741\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190316%2F59375741&d=WPnlDqr2f%2BBS7HOcP0JQkwAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=7233c567\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190316%2F59375741&h=3cbb4161\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190316/59375741</a>"},{"pid":"29528ef59c32a85fe5d3a6a7123ea810008ba5c7","tid":1064650,"uid":130695,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T17:06:23.000Z","msg":"中国賤種毒瘤為左錢真係殺自己老豆老母都可以"},{"pid":"9b3ae35b9e2e05ba88455fe244aa958f610ce216","tid":1064650,"uid":164838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T17:13:23.000Z","msg":"打貿易戰啊啦等我毒死你班仆街<br />\n利害了我的國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfbbed93eb9b0200215bf2d093e7cc7d8022ba99","tid":1064650,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-16T17:13:40.000Z","msg":"甜化襲擊<img src=\"/assets/